<section id="fs-id1167663635030" class="short-answer">
<title>Short Answer</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1167661432174">
<problem id="fs-id1167661432176">
<para id="fs-id1167663527492">Since we all have experienced many colds in our lifetime, why are we not resistant to future infections?</para>
</problem>
